OL,3,CGovernment appeal over Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful' ruling rejected
OL,6,FSenior judges have rejected an appeal
OL,7,Fby the former Northern Ireland
OL,8,FSecretary that his refusal to consider
OL,9,Fa public inquiry into the murder of
OL,10,Fthe Belfast solicitor Pat Finucane was
OL,11,Funlawful.
OL,13,FThe Court of Appeal also dismissed
OL,14,Fclaims by lawyers representing former
OL,15,FSecretary Chris Heaton-Harris that
OL,16,Fwidow Geraldine Finucane should not
OL,17,Fhave been awarded #5,000 in damages
OL,18,Ffor the continued delays in responding
OL,19,Fto her ongoing campaign.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G1/19
