OL,3,CGovernment appeal over Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful' ruling rejected
OL,6,FMr Finucane, 39, was shot dead by UDA
OL,7,Fgunmen in front of his wife and three
OL,8,Fchildren at their north Belfast home
OL,9,Fon February 12, 1989.
OL,11,FThe human rights lawyer was shot 14
OL,12,Ftimes while his wife Geraldine
OL,13,FFinucane was struck by a ricocheting
OL,14,Fbullet but she cheated serious injury.
OL,16,FThe Court of Appeal said on Thursday:
OL,17,F"This was a deliberately cruel and
OL,18,Fvicious murder designed to cause
OL,19,Fmaximum hurt and upset to the family
OL,20,Fand friends of Mr Finucane.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G2/19
OL,2,W/*% /*%/"-$+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
