OL,3,CGovernment appeal over Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful' ruling rejected
OL,6,F"Thirty five years later.....this
OL,7,Fmurder stands out as a truly barbarous
OL,8,Fact, the murder of a man in his own
OL,9,Fhome in the presence of his wife and
OL,10,Fhis very young children.
OL,12,F"Mr Finucane was a solicitor dedicated
OL,13,Fto protecting the rights of of his
OL,14,Fclients, regardless of their political
OL,15,For religious views.''
OL,17,FPrevious reviews had already
OL,18,Festablished that members of the
OL,19,Floyalist paramilitary gang involved in
OL,20,Fplanning and carrying out the
OL,21,Fassassination were British agents.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G3/19
