OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful' ruling rejected
OL,6,FBut Mrs Finucane and her family
OL,7,Fcontinued to lobby for a full public
OL,8,Finquiry to establish the scale of
OL,9,Fsecurity force collusion in one of the
OL,10,Fmost notorious killings of the
OL,11,FTroubles.
OL,13,FIn 2019 the UK Supreme Court declared
OL,14,Fthat earlier investigations into the
OL,15,Fmurder failed to meet standards
OL,16,Frequired by Article 2 of the European
OL,17,FConvention on Human Rights.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G4/19
