OL,6,FSince then, the lawyer's widow has
OL,7,Fmounted a series of legal battles over
OL,8,Fthe Government's response to those
OL,9,Ffindings.
OL,11,FIn November 2020 former Secretary of
OL,12,FState Brandon Lewis announced there
OL,13,Fwould not be a public inquiry at this
OL,14,Fstage because he wanted other police
OL,15,Freview processes to run their course.
OL,17,FHe was then ordered to pay #7,500
OL,18,Fdamages to Mrs Finucane for the
OL,19,Fexcessive delay in reaching that
OL,20,Fposition.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G5/19
