OL,6,FA further challenge was taken against
OL,7,Fthe legality of his decision to await
OL,8,Fthe outcome of reviews by the PSNI's
OL,9,FLegacy Investigations Branch and the
OL,10,FPolice Ombudsman for Northern Ireland
OL,11,F(PONI).
OL,13,FIn December 2022 High Court judge Mr
OL,14,FJustice Scoffield ruled the Government
OL,15,Fremains in breach of Article 2 by the
OL,16,Fongoing delay in completing a probe
OL,17,Fwhich meets those legal requirements.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}            G6/19
