OL,6,FHe quashed the decision not to
OL,7,Festablish a public inquiry at this
OL,8,Fstage, identifying an unlawful failure
OL,9,Fto reconsider its position following
OL,10,Fthe conclusion of a police review
OL,11,Fprocess.
OL,13,FIn early 2023, he ordered a further
OL,14,F#5,000 compensation to be paid to Mrs
OL,15,FFinucane for the "culpable delay" in
OL,16,FMr Heaton-Harris reaching a fresh
OL,17,Fconclusion on whether to establish a
OL,18,Fpublic inquiry.
