OL,6,F"The judge blurred the differences
OL,7,Fbetween public authorities, namely the
OL,8,FSecretary of State, PONI and PSNI," Mr
OL,9,FMcLaughlin submitted.
OL,11,FCiting a prompt completion of the
OL,12,Fpolice investigation and a change in
OL,13,Fattitude to waiting for the Ombudsman,
OL,14,Fhe contended that findings were
OL,15,Fwrongly made before any delay occurred.
OL,17,FMr McLaughlin said: "Just satisfaction
OL,18,Fdoes not require an award of damages."
