OL,6,FHowever, Mrs Finucane's counsel
OL,7,Finsisted the High Court had correctly
OL,8,Fidentified a legal error in Government
OL,9,Fthinking that the PSNI and PONI
OL,10,Fprocesses could potentially discharge
OL,11,Fthe Article 2 duty.
OL,13,FFiona Doherty KC said: "The Secretary
OL,14,Fof State who took this decision, and
OL,15,Fhis successor who now stands over it,
OL,16,Fare the latest in a long line of
OL,17,FSecretary of States who have taken
OL,18,Fdecisions to kick the can down the
OL,19,Froad in this case and run down the
OL,20,Fclock on it.
OL,26,@uD@XOU
