OL,6,F"This court should not allow them to
OL,7,Fdo it."
OL,9,FGiving the judgement of the court
OL,10,Ftoday (Thursday), Lord Justice Horner
OL,11,Fsaid: "We have no hesitation in
OL,12,Fconcluding that a second award of
OL,13,Fdamages (#5,000) is appropriate given
OL,14,Fthe culpable delay.
OL,16,F"The Secretary of State chose
OL,17,Foriginally to await the outcome of the
OL,18,F(PSNI and PONI) processes which were
OL,19,Fnotoriously beset with delay.
OL,26,@nD@AOUoD@GO]
