OL,6,F"It should have come as no surprise to
OL,7,Fthe Secretary of State that, for
OL,8,Fexample, the PONI process was
OL,9,Fhopelessly delayed.
OL,11,F"In all the circumstances we see no
OL,12,Fbasis to interfere with the award of
OL,13,F#5,000 damages for the period of
OL,14,FNovember 2020 to the date of Scoffield
OL,15,FJ's decision to afford satisfaction to
OL,16,FGeraldine Finucane.''
