OL,6,FThe appeal judges said they considered
OL,7,Fit would be "constitutionally
OL,8,Finappropriate'' to grant a mandatory
OL,9,Forder to establish a public inquiry in
OL,10,Fthe present circumstances.
OL,12,F"The Secretary of State took one
OL,13,Fparticular course of action when there
OL,14,Fare others which remain lawfully open
OL,15,Fto him.
OL,17,F"In the present case there are a
OL,18,Fnumber of options open to the
OL,19,FSecretary of State as to how he should
OL,20,Fgo about establishing an Article 2
OL,21,Fcompliant inquiry.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G15/19
