OL,3,CGovernment appeal over Finucane
OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful' ruling rejected
OL,6,F"However, should there be any undue
OL,7,Fdelay in setting up an Article 2
OL,8,Finquiry, then this court may be driven
OL,9,Fto make a mandatory order.''
OL,11,FThe Court of Appeal has now set out a
OL,12,Ftimetable for this: the parties have
OL,13,Fthree weeks from today (Thursday) to
OL,14,Fagree on an Article 2 compliant
OL,15,Fprocess for investigation of the
OL,16,Frelevant aspects of Mr Finucane's
OL,17,Fdeath.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G16/19
