OL,6,FIf there is no agreement, a further
OL,7,Fthree weeks will be granted to allow
OL,8,Fparties to submit their own proposal
OL,9,Fas to how an Article 2 compliant
OL,10,Finvestigation should be carried out.
OL,12,F"The court will endeavour to select
OL,13,Ffrom the two choices put forward by
OL,14,Fthe respective parties.
OL,1,W~k4 jw=hw1 hw}h7}j7}           G17/19
