OL,4,Cinquiry 'unlawful' ruling rejected
OL,6,F"In the unlikely event that the court
OL,7,Fis unable to choose either of the
OL,8,Fchoices put forward, the court
OL,9,Freserves the right to order its own
OL,10,FArticle 2 compliant process for the
OL,11,Finvestigation into the callous and
OL,12,Fbrutal murder of Mr Finucane as a last
OL,13,Fresort.
OL,15,F"For the reasons which we have
OL,16,Foutlined, this court dismisses the
OL,17,Fappeal of the Secretary of State.''
OL,19,FLord Justice Horner agreed to give the
OL,20,Fparties two weeks for the appropriate
OL,21,Forder of costs.
